snippet.title: Game Boy | Loopz (Gameplay)
snippet.description:
Name: Loopz
Developer: Milestone
Platform: Game Boy
Year: 1990
Genre: Puzzle

A puzzle game that is slightly similar to Tetris in the way that random pieces are given to you to fill the area. The major difference is that this game is just frustrating.
